{"tid":1705940,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發］今日兩點 有民間記者會","createTime":"2019-11-11T03:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T12:49:16.000Z","uid":22556,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b993de18cbd45647ca096d3c3766bc6099fc9348","tid":1705940,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"各大傳媒機構、採訪主任、編輯及記者：<br />\n<br />\n緊急採訪通知<br />\n<br />\n因應昨天晚上「八區開花」及今天早上「黎明行動」而出現的各區警暴情況，民間記者會將作出有關回應。現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年11月11日（星期一)<br />\n時間：下午2 時<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，如有查詢可向金先生查詢。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n採訪主任、編輯及記者<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2019年11月11日<br />\n<br />\nDear members of the press,<br />\n<br />\nRe: Invitation to an Emergency Press Conference<br />\n <br />\nThe Citizens&rsquo; Press Conference will be holding an emergency press conference to give response to the serial events of anti-human behaviour by the police with regards to the protests on the streets from yesterday evening onwards overnight and in the morning today.<br />\n<br />\nWe hereby cordially invite your organisation to attend our press conference. The details of the event are as follows:<br />\n  <br />\nDate: 11 Nov 2019<br />\nTime: 2:00 PM<br />\n<br />\nEmail: kim@citizenspc.org<br />\n <br />\nShould you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact our representative with the information as stated above.  Thank you for your kind attention.<br />\n <br />\nYours faithfully,<br />\nCitizens&rsquo; Press Conference"},{"pid":"3200bc95c720023c01cea81df5f17d18977d031d","tid":1705940,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9421b51889089548f0cc50a03b7e0571d82ef142","tid":1705940,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2bd943134a8b05c5bd69729fb73112bc971f82","tid":1